categories.label: Earnings report
categories.description: Periodic financial results: interim/quarter/half-year/year-end reports; may include KPIs, guidance commentary, and statutory statements.

categories.label: Share buyback
categories.description: Company repurchases of its own shares: program launches, extensions, updates, completions.

categories.label: Dividend
categories.description: Dividend declarations, proposals, changes, schedules (ex-date, record date, payment date).

categories.label: AGM/EGM & governance
categories.description: Annual/extraordinary general meeting notices and outcomes; board/nominations; bylaws changes; auditor matters.

categories.label: Capital raise / Rights issue
categories.description: Equity financing events: rights issues, directed issues, private placements, units/warrants; subscription details and use of proceeds.

categories.label: Managers' transactions (PDMR)
categories.description: Insider dealings by persons discharging managerial responsibilities (PDMR): purchases/sales/options exercises.

categories.label: Admission / Listing
categories.description: Listings and admissions to trading: first day of trading, uplistings, venue changes.

categories.label: Debt / Bond issue
categories.description: Debt financing: bonds/notes issuance, convertibles, syndicated loans, green/sustainability-linked bonds.

categories.label: Guidance / Outlook
categories.description: Forward-looking statements: guidance initiations/updates/withdrawals; trading updates; profit warnings.

categories.label: M&A
categories.description: Mergers, acquisitions, divestments, spin-offs, asset sales; includes deal terms, valuations, conditions, and timelines.

categories.label: Orders / Contracts
categories.description: Order wins, contract awards, framework agreements, renewals, significant tender results.

categories.label: Product / Launch / Partnership
categories.description: Product/service launches and upgrades; partnerships, collaborations, joint ventures, pilot programs.

categories.label: Personnel / Management change
categories.description: Executive and board changes: appointments, resignations, interim roles, succession plans.

categories.label: Sustainability / ESG
categories.description: Sustainability reports and initiatives; ESG targets/metrics; certifications; climate goals.

categories.label: Legal / Regulatory / Compliance
categories.description: Litigation, investigations, regulatory approvals/denials, fines/penalties, compliance disclosures.

categories.label: Credit & Ratings
categories.description: Issuer/instrument rating actions and outlooks by rating agencies; watch placements.

categories.label: Equity actions (non-buyback)
categories.description: Share splits/reverse splits, ticker/name changes, conversions, warrant exercises, share class changes.

categories.label: Labor / Workforce
categories.description: Workforce actions and relations: layoffs, plant closures, strikes/union matters, large hiring plans.

categories.label: Incidents / Controversies
categories.description: Operational incidents and controversies: safety/accidents, cybersecurity breaches, data/privacy incidents, sanctions.

categories.label: Delisting / Trading halt
categories.description: Delistings, trading suspensions/halts, market notices affecting trading status.

categories.label: Other / Corporate update
categories.description: General corporate updates that do not fit the above categories; housekeeping announcements.
